                {
                    "type": "text",
                    "value": "Reaching Sabbione involves traveling along a scenic mountain road that branches in the valley. The best time to visit is during spring and summer ("
                },
                {
                    "type": "text",
                    "class": "font-bold",
                    "value": "May to August"
                },
                {
                    "type": "text",
                    "value": "), when the valley‚Äôs natural beauty is at its peak. For those exploring the area, nearby villages such as "
                },
                {
                    "type": "link",
                    "target":"_blank",
                    "value": "Foroglio",
                    "url": "/posts/foroglio"
                },
                {
                    "type": "text",
                    "value": ", "
                },
                {
                    "type": "link",
                    "target":"_blank",
